<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[القِسْط]</span>: العدل،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه:</span> وَأَقِيمُوا الْوَزْنَ بِالْقِسْطِ <span class="c2">«٣»</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">والقِسط:</span> النصيب.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
